<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='0' id='t-0'>We've been told to go out on a limb
and say something surprising.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5786' id='t-5786'>So I'll try and do that,</span>
