<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='44176' id='t-44176'>Nowadays, this idea
has a dramatic name: Spaceship Earth.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='48819' id='t-48819'>And the idea there
