all we depend on,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58270' id='t-58270'>and we only get the one chance:
if we mess up our spaceship,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='61420' id='t-61420'>we've got nowhere else to go.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='63293' id='t-63293'>Now, the second thing
