<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1088041' id='t-1088041'>or problems in general.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1090000' id='t-1090000'>And with problems
that we are not aware of yet,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1092795' id='t-1092795'>the ability to put right -- not the sheer
good luck of avoiding indefinitely --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1098978' id='t-1098978'>is our only hope, not just
