<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1101795' id='t-1101795'>but of survival.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1103671' id='t-1103671'>So take two stone tablets,
