<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1111057' id='t-1111057'>On one of them, carve:
&quot;Problems are soluble.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1115763' id='t-1115763'>And on the other one, carve:
&quot;Problems are inevitable.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1120396' id='t-1120396'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
